.TH man 8 "22 Dec 2020" "1.0.1" "Hackadroid man page"

.SH NAME
Hackadroid 1.0.1

.SH DESCRIPTION
Hackadroid is an advanced automated android exploit tool that makes look android hacking simple.

.SH OPTIONS

1. Create a raw android payload, auto-hide script, start the listener, and makes a payload auto persistent.

2. Create an embed payload with the original apk, an start auto listener.

3. Makes an apk FUD, BY-PASS the play protect, and signs an apk with a key.

4. Sign an apk manually with mixplorer.

5. Decompile an Original apk

6. Recompile a file into an apk

7. Generate a persistent script for raw payload. (custom time delay)

8. Generate a persistent script for the embedded payload. (custom time delay)

9. Enable auto allow permissions in the payload.

10. Change the apk name and icon. (Disclaimer:- It only works with the raw payload)

11. Auto start listener on LAN. (Local Area Network)

12. Auto start listener over WAN. (Wide Area Network using ngrok)

13. Zipalign and compress the payload.

14. Dex to Java decompiler, decompile Dalvik bytecode to java classes.

For additional info, see: https://github.com/Bhaviktutorials

.SH SEE ALSO
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMhYgk0-nIHHtnRNkL9zpgQ/about

.SH BUGS
